      Where Qszt <> '0' And Qszt <> '9' And Qssj >= Kssj And Qssj < Jssj
      Union All
      Select Glbm, Sbbh, Yjsj, Qszt, Ljdw, Qssj, Sfcjlj
      From Vmc_Alarm_Pass
      Where Qszt <> '0' And Qszt <> '9' And Qssj >= Kssj And Qssj < Jssj;
    Cursor c_Alarm_Handle(Kssj Date, Jssj Date) Is
